1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,800
This rooster is Pelanpaw's son, the Dawnstar, he was called.

2
00:00:06,380 --> 00:00:12,140
Through him is forged the Weaver's Needle, the one that subdued the Many-Eyed Master.

3
00:00:12,880 --> 00:00:16,960
More than that, he once crowed a giant she-scorpion to death.

4
00:00:17,380 --> 00:00:20,120
Indeed, he is a bane to all insects.

